channel.title: Well not serious but, ive been wanting to know this for like 3 weeks now!
channel.description:
:mad: I got to "Mod Taharoks" ultimate server guide. And go to that jav download thing. I do what it says, download JDK 6... then it comes up with a load balls... then it starts to download.... i wait about 15 mins... and it says downloaded. Firstly i closed it... Then tried to compile my server. And it said You do not have java 5.0 or 6.0... Read Mo Taharoks tutorial... (blah blah blah...) I uninstalled it... Downloaded it again, but this time i restarted my comp, to see if that would help... And it didn't... SOOOOO....
Anyone have any ideas??? PLEASE??? :( :( :( :(
